#                                                                                                            #
#  Librarian                                                                                                 #
#   Might of Heroes for the Chaplain to get him to S9/T7, Psychic Fortress to give 5++ to Outriders          #
#   Jump Pack to keep up with the Outriders/Chaplain                                                         #
#   The Beacon Angelis in the event that some unit needs to exist somewhere else /right now/.                #
#    e.g. Summoning the Apothecary from the Indomitus part of the field to the Outriders/Chaplain            #
#                                                                                                            #
#  Primaris Chaplain                                                                                         #
#   Extraordinarily difficult to kill hyper mobile beatstick                                                 #
#   Defensive profile - T7 | 3+ | 4++ | 4+++ | Primaris/Transhuman available                                 #
#   Offensive Profile - 7 Attacks | 2+ WS | S9 | AP-1/2 | 4D                                                 #
#   Can replace "The Imperiums Sword" with several options from "Paragon of their Chapter"                   #
#    Black Templars for 6" Heroic Intervention, Raven Guard to redeploy during any movement step,            #
#    Space Wolves for +1 attacks/hit/wound vs Monsters & Vehicles, Crimson Fists to revive on a 4+ on death  #
#                                                                                                            #
##############################################################################################################

