##############################################################################################################
#                                                                                                            #
#  Fortis Kill Team                                                                                          # 
#                                                                                                            #
#   Furor - Most likely unit to be thrown into enemy Troop units (without wielding Lightning Claws)          #
#   Intercessor squad will hold a 'safe' backline objective, provide supplemental fire on low T units        #
#   Outriders move up with Chaplain to hold a forward objective; quite durable with Transhuman & 5++ | 5+++  #
#   Will be most likely target of +1 Wound from the Chaplain                                                 #
#                                                                                                            #
#  Proteus Kill Team                                                                                         #
#                                                                                                            #
#   DW Vets provide supplemental fire while being relatively durable on a back objective                     #
#    Investigate Signal objective goblins                                                                    #
#   VanVets w/ Thunder hammers wound most targets on 3's, Aquila gives rerolling wound rolls of 1            #
#    Stick near Fortis/Chaplain squad to take advantage of Chaplain full melee rerolls to counter -1 hit     #
#    Outriders better at horde clearing than vehicle/monsters, good pairing for hammer VV's                  #
#    Keep hidden and use to screen, keep within ~16" of Outriders/Chaplain as counter-punch                  #
#                                                                                                            #
##############################################################################################################

