#                                                                                                            #
#  Primaris Captain                                                                                          #
#   Exists primarily for reroll 1's and to carry Dominus Aegis for the 5++ aura for Indomitor Kill Team      #
#   Decent melee counterpunch with Master-crafted power sword                                                #
#   Also can give reroll 1's to wound to Indomitor for Fast Attack & Elite killing                           #
#   Honestly the Primaris Captain from Indomitus looks really damn cool                                      #
#                                                                                                            #
#  Primaris Librarian                                                                                        #                  
#   6+ WC for 5+++ cast for Indomitor or Fortis, depending on locations of each and Apothecary location      #
#   Reliquary of Gathalamor puts enemy Psykers at -1 within 18 and -2 within 12, with perils on every fail   #
#    Will often be center table with Outriders on a flank, providing sizeable coverage area                  #
#    +prevalence of newly buffed Thousand Sons and Grey Knights...                                           #
#   Premorphic Resonance decent vs lower armor attackers, makes Indomitor overwatch quite scary              #
#    Fantastic for hammer VV's squad                                                                         #
#                                                                                                            #
#                                                                                                            #
##############################################################################################################

