#  Proteus Kill Team is another objective goblin / support & counterpunch unit                               #
#   No unit specialty because Lightning Claws make redundant                                                 #
#    Can replace Storm Shields with claws & move with Indomitor under Librarian Shroud buff                  #
#   Indomitor better at clearing monsters/vehicles than hordes, making for a good pairing with CS/LC vets    #
#    Similarly useful for screening @ counter punch                                                          #
#                                                                                                            #
